'''2015年緬甸議會選舉'''於2015年11月8日舉行<ref name="GE">{{cite news |url=https://www.dvb.no/news/general-election-will-be-nov-dec-2015-says-ec-chairman-burma-myanmar/38722 |title=General Election will be Nov- Dec 2015, says EC chairman |date=20 March 2014 |agency=DVB News |accessdate=13 April 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413142847/https://www.dvb.no/news/general-election-will-be-nov-dec-2015-says-ec-chairman-burma-myanmar/38722 |archive-date=2014-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。此次选举是自缅甸独立以来第五次自由的多党民主选举，也是缅甸间隔25年首次公开竞争的国会大选。這次選舉由全[[緬甸|緬甸]]的各個選區改選出除了[[緬甸軍事|軍方]]委派的25%議席以外的所有[[緬甸聯邦議會|緬甸聯邦議會]]上下院議員（498席）。

== 準備 ==
緬甸執政黨[[聯邦鞏固與發展黨|聯邦鞏固與發展黨]]已經推出了其競選策略，該黨稱他們將會在2010年當選的選區進行競選活動。<ref name="mizzima1">{{cite web |url=http://www.mizzima.com/mizzima-news/politics/item/10768-political-parties-gear-up-for-2015-election |title=Political parties gear up for 2015 election |publisher=Mizzima.com |date=15 October 2013 |accessdate=29 December 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228110203/http://mizzima.com/mizzima-news/politics/item/10768-political-parties-gear-up-for-2015-election |archivedate=2013-12-28 }}</ref>

至於反對黨[[全國民主聯盟_(緬甸)|全國民主聯盟]]則表示，雖然按現行憲法其黨首[[昂山素姬|昂山素姬]]無法參選總統，但他們仍然會進行競選活動。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.startribune.com/world/237811691.html |title=Suu Kyi's party says it will contest 2015 Myanmar election even if constitution is not amended |work=Star Tribune |accessdate=29 December 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230233548/http://www.startribune.com/world/237811691.html |archivedate=2013-12-30 }}</ref>

[[緬甸民族團結黨|緬甸民族團結黨]]則表示，他們會保住2010年贏得的議席，並爭取贏取更多議席。國家民主力量則表示他們會參加多至200個议席的競選。各個少數民族政黨爲應對大選，將會合併成一個「緬甸聯邦聯盟黨」(FUP)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2013-06/14/c_124855427.htm|title=緬甸15個少數民族政黨合成一個政黨 應對2015大選|publisher=新華網|accessdate=2016-05-18|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305062123/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2013-06/14/c_124855427.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

緬甸大選委員會公佈，當地91個參選政黨和310個無黨籍人士會參與本屆選舉<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mmgpmedia.com/local-news/11126-%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E8%8E%B7%E6%89%B9%E5%8F%82%E9%80%89%E5%80%99%E9%80%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%B16074%E4%BA%BA|title=全国获批参选候选人共6074人|date=2015-10-08|work=金凤凰|accessdate=2015-10-10|location=仰光|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305044753/http://www.mmgpmedia.com/local-news/11126-%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E8%8E%B7%E6%89%B9%E5%8F%82%E9%80%89%E5%80%99%E9%80%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%B16074%E4%BA%BA|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 選情分析 ==
本來緬甸總統[[登盛|登盛]]有可能在2015年選舉結束，任期屆滿後不連任下台。前[[國家和平與發展委員會|軍政府]]第三號人物，人民院院長[[瑞曼|瑞曼]]被外界視為思想開明的人物，也曾經是最有可能繼承登盛的人選。昂山素姬曾經和他達成協議，昂山素姬支持瑞曼成爲總統候選人，以換取憲法改革。但瑞曼最終卻失去了軍方支持，他的黨職在2015年8月12日被免除<ref name=BBC1/><ref>{{cite news |last=Krause |first=Flavia |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-03/myanmar-s-leader-may-step-aside-after-2015-elections-aide-says.html |title=Myanmar's Leader May Step Aside After 2015 Elections, Aide Says |publisher=Bloomberg |date=3 May 2012 |accessdate=29 December 2013 |archive-date=2014-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101054620/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-03/myanmar-s-leader-may-step-aside-after-2015-elections-aide-says.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://time.com/3995708/burma-myanmar-shwe-mann-thein-sein-purge-elections-southeast-asia/ |work=Time |first=Charlie |last=Campbell |title=Burmese President Purges Party Chief |date=13 August 2015 |accessdate=2015-10-10 |archive-date=2015-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151019003534/http://time.com/3995708/burma-myanmar-shwe-mann-thein-sein-purge-elections-southeast-asia/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。反對黨領袖[[昂山素姬|昂山素姬]]重申她想成為下任緬甸總統，但如果不修改憲法的話，她是沒有參選總統資格的<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-pacific-22812540 |title=Aung San Suu Kyi: 'I want to be Burma's president' |publisher=BBC |date=7 June 2013 |accessdate=29 December 2013 |archive-date=2015-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150323210249/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-pacific-22812540 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，聯邦國會已於2015年6月15日否決大部分憲法修訂案，令昂山素姬無法競逐總統職務<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/06/25/myanmars-parliament-blocks-changes-to-constitution|title=Myanmar's parliament blocks changes to constitution - US News|work=US News & World Report|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2015-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150731092645/http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/06/25/myanmars-parliament-blocks-changes-to-constitution|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

